overview: “Mike Feliciano leads the business development and sales initiatives for Tyfone, bringing over 22 years of technology, software, and financial services experience to the firm. Throughout his career, Mikeâ€™s primary focus has been electronic payment processing. Before joining Tyfone, Mike was President & CEO of Everlink Payment Services, a Canadian transaction switching company, where he was responsible for the strategic and business management of the company. His previous experience includes serving as Senior Vice President & Division Executive of the Electronic Payments Division at eFunds. In that role, he oversaw all aspects of the software, processing, and government businesses. His other positions include Vice President & General Manager EFT Processing for the NYCE Corporation, Regional Manager, Electronic Commerce Division at Electronic Data Systems, and Vice President of Marketing for the Florida Credit Union League Service Group. Mike has a BS degree in finance from Florida State University in Tallahassee.” (Source: Tyfone)
